Package com.id.droneapi.mock.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DirectionNotFound
    Fired if the Direction provided doesn't match with any direction supported
    DuplicatedAdjacentNode
    Fired if there are two node with the same id/coords
    NoAdjacentNode
    Exception fired if the required Adjacent not is not found
    NodeAlreadyAdded
    Fired if a same node already exists in the UrmanizationMatrix
    NodeAlreadyAddedAsAdjacent
    Fired if the adjacent node has been already added to the UrbanizationMatrix
    NodeNotFound
    Fired if the node required is not found
